1618889459.text: "The accurately ordered cell cycle also includes the timely degradation of many regulatory proteins via ubiquitin mediated proteolysis; the SCF complexes represent a big family of ubiquitin ligases that determine the abundance of cell cycle regulatory proteins; Skp2 promotes the ubiquitinylation of the CDKIs, p21, and p27, thereby enhancing CDK2 activation at the G1/S border [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR]."
